description: [``botocore``] API model updated in Amazon Cognito
[``botocore``] Add support for deleting Queues and Routing Profiles.
[``botocore``] Added LunCount to the response object of DescribeStorageSystemResourcesResponse, LunCount represents the number of LUNs on a storage system resource.
[``botocore``] Enhanced PostgreSQL target endpoint settings for providing Babelfish support.

[``botocore``] This release adds support for the C7gn and Hpc7g instances. C7gn instances are powered by AWS Graviton3 processors and the fifth-generation AWS Nitro Cards. Hpc7g instances are powered by AWS Graviton 3E processors and provide up to 200 Gbps network bandwidth.
[``botocore``] Amazon FSx for NetApp ONTAP now supports SnapLock, an ONTAP feature that enables you to protect your files in a volume by transitioning them to a write once, read many (WORM) state.
[``botocore``] Documentation updates for AWS Identity and Access Management (IAM).
[``botocore``] Adds categories to MediaTailor channel assembly alerts
[``botocore``] This release provides ability to customers to change schema associated with their datasets in Amazon Personalize
[``botocore``] This release adds support for deployment history for Proton provisioned resources
[``botocore``] S3 Inventory now supports Object Access Control List and Object Owner as available object metadata fields in inventory reports.
[``botocore``] Amazon SageMaker Canvas adds WorkspeceSettings support for CanvasAppSettings
